<figureCitation box="[871,986,1479,1501]" captionStart="Figs" captionStartId="4.[197,237,834,853]" captionTargetBox="[205,1177,183,813]" captionTargetId="figure-512@4.[173,1193,155,850]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="Figs. 13–18. Third instars of Macrodactylus nigripes (13–15) and Macrodactylus ocreatus (16–18). 13) Head, frontal view; 14) Epipharynx; 15) Raster. 16) Head, frontal view; 17) Epipharynx; 18) Raster. Scale bars = 1 mm." pageId="3" pageNumber="196">Figs. 13–15</figureCitation>
